The key is to save mana and use ur bow to take it down. If you dot or DD you will run out of mana before the giant dies, root or snare breaks and soon you break too.<br>
Snare is a much more controlable mean of slow down. Just know the area where you kite it down you dont want to pull a train on yourself. In DL I perfer to kite up and down along the south wall of KC.<br>
This is ok for fun and loot but too slow a method for xp.<br>
<br>
Tuline <br>
